EC2:
"Amazon EC2 is a scalable virtual compute service.
We can launch instances with required OS, RAM, and CPU.
It supports any language-based application like Node.js, Python, Java.
Billing is per second/hour while running.
When stopped, only storage billing applies.
When terminated, compute billing stops completely."

